  "description": "A CodeSystem supplement that adds consumer information and clinical reference URLs to SNOMED CT pathology test concepts. Provides links to Pathology Tests Explained (a consumer-friendly resource) and the RCPA Manual (a clinical reference for pathology test selection and interpretation).",
